261
00:15:57,958 --> 00:16:00,667
this hospital is committed
to providing a safe environment

262
00:16:00,750 --> 00:16:03,292
Safe environment for all of its employees…

263
00:16:06,417 --> 00:16:08,417
Free from sexual harassment.

264
00:16:23,708 --> 00:16:27,500
<i>I am sharing my story on a public forum</i>

265
00:16:27,583 --> 00:16:30,000
<i>because I want everyone to know.</i>

266
00:16:30,083 --> 00:16:33,875
<i>I was Dr Geetika Sen's trusting patient</i>

267
00:16:35,667 --> 00:16:38,458
