785
00:57:14,792 --> 00:57:19,833
I can cook, but you will have to eat it.

786
00:57:22,917 --> 00:57:24,417
<i>Carol is not anonymous.</i>

787
00:57:25,542 --> 00:57:27,583
We will no longer be able to relocate.

788
