I have to think about myself, too.

796
00:58:10,708 --> 00:58:13,042
After all, I have a reputation to build.

797
00:58:44,417 --> 00:58:45,542
What the hell?

798
00:58:49,250 --> 00:58:51,417
- Sir, I tried, but…
- But what?

799
00:58:52,750 --> 00:58:54,083
Whose car is this?

800
